messages.msg: Welcome to our site! If you are looking for prayer or someone to chat with, reply to this message or email us at prayer@fightlust.com

I want to renounce and repent of all sexual sins that I have been involved in I repent of allowing my body to be used as an instrument of unrighteousness I pray that all demonic forces behind sexual immorality would be destroyed by the power of God in my life I repent for not allowing God to be the Lord of my life and obeying the lust of the flesh I ask for forgiveness for allowing my sexual desires to rule over me I repent for allowing darkness to take the place of light in my life

It's wonderful that you're seeking to renounce and repent of those struggles. Here's a prayer you can use:

"Heavenly Father, I come before you today through the blood of Jesus Christ. I renounce all sexual sins that I have been involved in, including allowing my body to be used as an instrument of unrighteousness. I pray that all demonic forces behind sexual immorality would be destroyed by Your power in my life. I repent for not allowing You to be the Lord of my life and for obeying the lust of the flesh. I ask for Your forgiveness for allowing my sexual desires to rule over me and for letting darkness take the place of light in my life. Fill me with Your Holy Spirit and guide me towards purity and righteousness. In Jesus' name, Amen."

If you need further support or resources, feel free to ask!

I pray that all sexual sin in my life be exposed to the light I pray that light would expel the darkness of sexual immorality I renounce all evil urges that the enemy would try to bring into my mind from this day forward I pray that all those evil urges would always run into the light and be compelled to flee from this day forward I repent for leaving the path of holiness and allowing myself to influenced by demonic forces especially in my sexuality

That's a powerful prayer! Here's a prayer you can use based on your intentions:

"Heavenly Father, I pray that all sexual sin in my life be exposed to the light. I ask that Your light would expel the darkness of sexual immorality. I renounce all evil urges that the enemy tries to bring into my mind from this day forward. I pray that all those evil urges would always run into the light and be compelled to flee from me. I repent for leaving the path of holiness and for allowing myself to be influenced by demonic forces, especially in my sexuality. Fill me with Your Holy Spirit and guide me back to a life of purity and righteousness. In Jesus' name, Amen."

If you need more support or resources, just let me know!

That's a heartfelt prayer! Here’s a prayer you can use based on your intentions:

I confess that there is only one way to You, and that is through Jesus Christ. I repent of all false beliefs that I have held about Your Word and for ever believing in any other gospel other than the true and living Word of God. I pray that from this day forward, my spirit, will, and heart will only crave, desire, and follow the true Word of God. Fill me with Your truth and guide me in Your ways. In Jesus' name, Amen."

If you need further assistance or resources, feel free to reach out!
